content: Thanks for meeting with me today, Luna. I'm really excited to be here.

Well, Felipe, we'll see if that excitement lasts after a few long shifts dealing with grumpy customers and folding endless stacks of shirts. But I'm glad to have you here. Let's get started with the interview!
Hello Luna, looking forward to this interview.
Hello Felipe, it's always refreshing to see someone looking forward to an interview. Hopefully, by the end of this, you'll still have that enthusiasm. Let's dive right in, shall we?
